Disability checks
never are confiscated
unless there's an unpaid bill.

44:55.032 --> 44:56.526
Does an unpaid bill
sound familiar?

44:56.561 --> 44:59.298
I've been over this
with the VA helpline.
Twice.

44:59.333 --> 45:01.399
I called
the-the VA crisis-line.

45:01.434 --> 45:03.775
I called, uh, Lincoln Tech.

45:03.810 --> 45:08.010
I been down to the office,
but you-- you know what
the problem is, ma'am?

45:08.045 --> 45:10.342
-You don't write nothing down.

45:10.377 --> 45:13.081
If you put that pen
to that paper, you would
have that information.

45:13.116 --> 45:15.083
Please, please
don't raise your voice,
Mr. Easley.

45:15.118 --> 45:17.052
It's just a suggestion.

45:17.087 --> 45:19.219
-I ain't raising my voice.
