Two.

45:24.930 --> 45:26.864
I've been ill.

45:26.899 --> 45:29.933
I had to take leave,
so I'm reliant
on this disability check.

45:31.431 --> 45:35.004
Ma'am, don't dip into my money
and call it a day.

45:38.372 --> 45:41.076
You gonna have me on--
on the streets.

45:42.849 --> 45:44.112
I'm a grown man.

45:45.181 --> 45:47.016
I won't be able to feed myself.

45:57.061 --> 46:00.227
We have programs
for those who are food
and housing insecure.

46:01.967 --> 46:05.364
You can call the helpline
or you can take a number
and wait in that line.

46:12.340 --> 46:13.471
Okay.

46:18.610 --> 46:19.513
Thank you.

46:23.384 --> 46:24.416
Next.

46:47.672 --> 46:51.080
Yeah, they said I still owe,
which is a damn lie.

46:51.115 --> 46:52.213
It's a lie.

46:53.282 --> 46:57.548
That must've been
very frustrating.

46:57.583 --> 47:00.353
<i>It was. I'm not a psychopath.</i>

47:00.388 --> 47:02.993
I know what I do
and I know what I don't.

47:03.028 --> 47:04.357
I know, I hear you.
<i>Truth.</i>

47:10.596 --> 47:11.661
I hear you, Brian.

47:11.696 --> 47:13.102
Do you?

47:15.370 --> 47:18.239
What station is this again?
<i>WSB-TV, why?</i>

47:18.274 --> 47:21.275
<i>We're recording right now,</i>
<i>we live, on TV?</i>

47:22.608 --> 47:24.047
Um...

47:24.984 --> 47:26.181
I'll take that as a no.

47:26.216 --> 47:27.512
<i>Well, what it means is that</i>

47:27.547 --> 47:30.317
<i>we're not gonna exploit you</i>
<i>for ratings.</i>

47:30.352 --> 47:34.321
<i>So we're gonna wait--</i>
I need the world to see
what's happening here.

47:34.356 --> 47:36.422
Can you do that for me,
ma'am?

47:36.457 --> 47:37.654
Can we do that?

47:37.689 --> 47:39.029
<i>Please.</i>

47:40.329 --> 47:42.362
Major Riddick,
are we allowed to go live?

47:42.397 --> 47:45.530
Hey, uh, put the TV on WSB.

47:47.369 --> 47:49.138
<i>We're working</i>
<i>to get you two out.</i>

47:49.173 --> 47:52.372
<i>Don't try nothing.</i>
<i>Just stay put until</i>
<i>we get there.</i>

47:54.409 --> 47:58.246
<i>Our priority</i>
<i>is the protection of life</i>
<i>inside the dwelling.</i>

47:58.281 --> 48:02.283
<i>We're now running</i>
<i>a multi-agency operation</i>
<i>to get these hostages out safe.</i>

48:02.318 --> 48:05.484
-<i> At what point</i>
<i>do you have to change...</i>
-Ma'am.

48:06.355 --> 48:08.223
You have
a police officer on air,

48:08.258 --> 48:10.720
but the man who the situation
is about is nowhere to be seen.

48:10.755 --> 48:13.426
-Does that make sense to you?
-Have you got kids?

48:13.461 --> 48:15.197
You know I do.

48:15.232 --> 48:18.134
<i>Well, then you know why</i>
<i>you called here first.</i>

48:20.039 --> 48:21.434
Why'd I do that?

48:21.469 --> 48:26.175
Because we are
not going to let
your children--

48:26.210 --> 48:28.078
yours and mine--

48:28.113 --> 48:31.312
<i>watch you blow up that bank</i>
<i>on the air.</i>

48:31.347 --> 48:35.250
<i>The suspect, I should say,</i>
<i>is workable...</i>

48:35.285 --> 48:37.989
<i>I understand he is a local.</i>
<i>Yes, but I cannot confirm that.</i>

48:38.024 --> 48:39.188
<i>And what can you tell us...</i>

48:39.223 --> 48:40.992
So what's it look like
out there?

48:41.027 --> 48:42.752
<i> It may have something</i>
<i>to do with this outcome.</i>

48:42.787 --> 48:45.260
<i>I do not have information</i>
<i>regarding that at this moment.</i>

48:45.295 --> 48:47.163
They got a lot of people
waiting for me?

49:09.121 --> 49:10.153
Hello?

49:10.188 --> 49:12.221
<i>Cassandra Easley?</i>
Yes.

49:12.256 --> 49:15.356
<i>I'm Agent Jackman of the FBI.</i>
<i>Can you confirm</i>
<i>your current address?</i>

49:24.070 --> 49:26.301
<i>Do you have any other family</i>
<i>we could contact?</i>

49:27.634 --> 49:30.767
<i>My brother. But we don't talk.</i>

49:30.802 --> 49:32.043
Nothing.

49:33.376 --> 49:35.376
Hey, everybody.

49:35.411 --> 49:37.444
Riddick, right?
Yes, sir.
Real pleasure.

49:37.479 --> 49:39.578
Fine job out here.
Got everything you need?

49:39.613 --> 49:44.088
Yeah, snipers are in place.
Area's clean.
Uh, no sign of an accomplice.

49:44.123 --> 49:46.453
Now that Bernard's here,
we're ready to rock and roll.

49:46.488 --> 49:49.291
Good, good. Atlanta's
watching you today, son.

49:49.326 --> 49:51.425
-<i> Okay, this is good.</i>
-No pressure.

49:51.460 --> 49:53.526
<i>...trying to figure out</i>
<i>what's happening over there...</i>

49:53.561 --> 49:56.628
Let's just give him
five more minutes.
Let him wind down.

49:57.796 --> 49:59.367
Lisa...

50:02.768 --> 50:04.537
can I ask you a question?

50:05.606 --> 50:06.638
<i>Sure.</i>

50:10.116 --> 50:11.442
Is life hard for you?

50:15.517 --> 50:17.748
It's hard for everybody I know.
They--

50:19.719 --> 50:21.521
Is it really hard, like--

50:23.855 --> 50:26.394
Seems like everywhere I turn,
they--

50:32.237 --> 50:34.567
You know, my own brother
put a hit out on me.

50:37.671 --> 50:41.310
How did he, uh...

50:41.345 --> 50:43.543
I don't know.
I don't know. They said--

50:44.579 --> 50:46.744
They said he put
20,000 on my head.

50:48.253 --> 50:49.681
Brian, who said that?

50:49.716 --> 50:51.782
The streets is talking.

50:56.525 --> 51:00.560
He a part
of some secret society,
some cult like that.

51:00.595 --> 51:05.136
I don't really mess with him,
but they real, real sick people.

51:06.205 --> 51:08.502
Just four kidnapping attempts
on me last year.

51:08.537 --> 51:10.702
You know that? Four.

51:13.509 --> 51:14.739
<i> Are you sure?</i>

51:15.841 --> 51:17.478
<i> Am I sure?</i>

51:17.513 --> 51:19.117
We gotta stop this.

51:19.647 --> 51:20.811
<i> All right.</i>

51:22.254 --> 51:23.253
<i>Uh...</i>

51:23.651 --> 51:25.156
<i>Well...</i>

51:25.191 --> 51:26.355
You know what?

51:28.392 --> 51:29.622
I don't need a translator.

51:31.296 --> 51:33.824
I need to be on the camera.
Can you send somebody down here?

51:33.859 --> 51:37.894
Oh. Well, we have, um--
we have reporters out there.

51:37.929 --> 51:40.765
Mark said that it can work, uh--
You can meet him at a window.

51:40.800 --> 51:42.767
Yeah, we have reporters
out there, uh--

51:42.802 --> 51:45.737
<i>But how would we do it?</i>
<i>Is there a window...</i>

51:49.413 --> 51:51.644
<i> Ma'am, ma'am,</i>
<i>I'm not going near the window.</i>

51:51.679 --> 51:53.547
I do not want to get shot.

51:53.582 --> 51:56.748
-Coming through. Coming through!
-Hey!

51:56.783 --> 51:59.487
Sir!
Stay away from that bank.

51:59.522 --> 52:02.325
Tell your reporters
to stay the fuck off the phone.

52:02.360 --> 52:04.195
You're jeopardizing
his life and yours.

52:04.230 --> 52:07.264
That reporter--
You have been warned.

52:10.269 --> 52:12.500
As you can see,
this is a very
volatile situation.

52:12.535 --> 52:15.965
Don't you have a--
a long lens that zoom in
that you can see me with?

52:16.000 --> 52:18.869
I'm asking about a long lens.
Oh, long lens. Let me ask.

52:18.904 --> 52:20.574
We're checking on that for you.

52:20.609 --> 52:23.478
<i>Because that's a good idea.</i>
<i>Keep you safe.</i>

52:23.513 --> 52:25.810
Major.
I can't prevent that.
Hold on.

52:25.845 --> 52:29.913
Major. We haven't even talked
to this guy yet, and you're
letting them film him?

52:29.948 --> 52:31.948
What are we doing here?
What is this?

52:31.983 --> 52:35.556
What is what?
You're highly emotional,
Sergeant.

52:37.021 --> 52:39.725
Sir, my professional opinion?

52:39.760 --> 52:41.793
This some bullshit.

52:41.828 --> 52:43.531
May I start
a direct line of communication

52:43.566 --> 52:45.731
so someone trained
in this field
can talk to him?

52:45.766 --> 52:47.931
<i>I'm at North Park,</i>
<i>trying to divert traffic...</i>

52:50.441 --> 52:51.473
Just push redial.

52:54.544 --> 52:56.247
Yeah, I'm back.

52:56.282 --> 52:58.678
<i>Suspect exits the bank,</i>
<i>he will not leave the sidewalk.</i>

52:58.713 --> 53:00.416
<i>Are you clear on that?</i>

53:00.451 --> 53:02.880
<i>Suspect exits the bank,</i>
<i>he will not leave the sidewalk.</i>

53:04.917 --> 53:06.851
Can you
send somebody down here?

53:10.857 --> 53:11.955
Ma'am, ma'am,

53:11.990 --> 53:14.562
I'm not going down there, okay?

53:14.597 --> 53:17.367
I do not wanna get sniped.

53:17.402 --> 53:19.600
Okay, I kinda hear him
talking in the background.

53:19.635 --> 53:21.965
<i>He's still on</i>
<i>with the media, right?</i>

53:22.902 --> 53:24.000
Uh-huh.

53:24.035 --> 53:25.573
We don't play that around here,

53:25.608 --> 53:26.937
I'll tell you that much.

53:39.655 --> 53:41.589
<i> Brian.</i>

53:41.624 --> 53:43.294
<i>Brian, calm down.</i>

53:45.023 --> 53:47.628
<i>I need to be on camera, okay?</i>

53:49.764 --> 53:51.335
<i> Yeah. Yeah.</i>

53:57.904 --> 54:00.311
Look, they're telling me

54:00.346 --> 54:03.512
that it's just going to
take a minute to locate
the camera equipment we need.

54:03.547 --> 54:05.712
But it's coming. Okay?

54:05.747 --> 54:07.351
You're lying.
<i>No, sir.</i>

54:07.386 --> 54:08.979
You're lying to me right now.
I can hear you.

54:09.014 --> 54:11.014
You're lying,
I hear it in your voice.
<i>No. No.</i>

54:11.049 --> 54:12.719
You know what,
we're gonna wrap this up.

54:12.754 --> 54:14.325
<i>No, no, no.</i>
We're gonna wrap this up.

54:14.360 --> 54:16.327
<i>Don't do that. Hey...</i>

54:16.758 --> 54:18.494
Wait, my, uh--

54:18.529 --> 54:22.091
God. Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!

54:22.126 --> 54:23.829
That's all I've been told!

54:23.864 --> 54:25.061
Is to wait!
<i>Brian.</i>

54:25.096 --> 54:26.700
What do I need to do

54:26.735 --> 54:30.000
to get the attention
that I need right now?

54:30.035 --> 54:31.507
Right now!

54:31.971 --> 54:33.839
Right now, ma'am!

54:33.874 --> 54:36.105
Brian. Brian, calm down.

54:36.140 --> 54:38.646
<i>Calm down.</i>
Is this what I need to do?

54:38.681 --> 54:40.648
<i>No. We're gonna--</i>

54:40.683 --> 54:43.354
<i>We're going to take care--</i>
This what I need to do? Okay.

54:43.389 --> 54:45.356
Okay.

54:45.391 --> 54:47.457
Is this what you need?

54:47.492 --> 54:51.054
Is this all the motivation
you need to get me
what I need?

54:51.089 --> 54:53.397
You have hostages
in here, ma'am!

54:54.158 --> 54:55.795
Hostages, and they scared!

54:55.830 --> 54:57.995
They scared
for their damn lives!
<i>Brian...</i>

54:58.030 --> 55:00.503
I need a phone call!
<i>Brian,</i>

55:00.538 --> 55:02.769
you have
my undivided attention.

55:02.804 --> 55:05.772
I don't need
your undivided attention!

55:05.807 --> 55:08.775
I need the attention of the VA!

55:08.810 --> 55:10.414
Not you!

55:12.847 --> 55:15.716
-Yeah, we're ready.
<i>All right. We're gonna do this.</i>

55:15.751 --> 55:16.783
You got it.

55:16.818 --> 55:17.916
Brian...

55:20.151 --> 55:22.151
<i>Now, ma'am, can you get me</i>
<i>this phone call?</i>

55:22.186 --> 55:24.791
<i>Hey, Brian...</i>
Or do I have to
blow this bitch up?

55:24.826 --> 55:29.961
<i>Brian, they just told me</i>
<i>the negotiator wants to call you</i>
<i>on this line, like, right now.</i>

55:30.964 --> 55:32.469
Negotiator
is on the phone, ma'am?

55:32.504 --> 55:33.866
You're not lying to me
right now?

55:33.901 --> 55:35.967
The negotiator
is on the phone?
<i>Yeah.</i>

55:36.002 --> 55:38.706
'Cause we can't go
back and forth no more.
We can't do that.

55:38.741 --> 55:43.579
No, no, no. So-- So--
You go talk to him.
And then you call me back.

55:47.816 --> 55:48.848
Okay.

55:52.183 --> 55:54.051
Okay, that's--
that's a start.

55:54.086 --> 55:55.525
That's a start.

55:58.629 --> 56:00.123
-Ring him through.
-Okay.

56:00.158 --> 56:02.026
Yeah.
She's doing it right now.

56:05.196 --> 56:06.569
I apologize.

56:16.482 --> 56:17.943
What are we going to report?

56:19.012 --> 56:20.077
Everything.

56:20.112 --> 56:21.848
<i> And we're live.</i>

56:21.883 --> 56:25.852
<i>Five, four, three, two...</i>

56:25.887 --> 56:29.053
<i> Breaking news,</i>
<i>we have a hostage standoff</i>
<i>at a Wells Fargo</i>

56:29.088 --> 56:31.858
with Team 2 coverage from
our news chopper in the air,

56:31.893 --> 56:33.959
and a team on the ground.

56:33.994 --> 56:38.535
The suspect made exclusive
contact with our seasoned
producer, Lisa Larson.

56:38.570 --> 56:42.198
<i>This is</i> Channel 2 Action News.
<i>We start with Keith James</i>
<i>live in Marietta.</i>

56:43.905 --> 56:46.202
We appear to have
a very volatile
situation here,

56:46.237 --> 56:49.777
where a man
has barricaded himself
inside a bank with...

56:49.812 --> 56:54.881
<i>...an explosive device</i>
<i>and a story that</i>
<i>he needs to have told.</i>

56:54.916 --> 56:59.149
<i>Police are no longer</i>
<i>calling this a robbery,</i>
<i>rather a hostage situation.</i>

56:59.184 --> 57:02.724
<i>And ten to 15 minutes ago,</i>
<i>the sheriff's SWAT team arrived.</i>

57:04.057 --> 57:05.958
<i>Keith, thank you.</i>
<i>And now to Mark Cavanaugh.</i>

57:05.993 --> 57:09.060
<i>He's live on the other side</i>
<i>of this standoff with police.</i>

57:09.095 --> 57:11.931
<i>Mark, what can you tell us</i>
<i>about the suspect?</i>

57:13.935 --> 57:17.233
<i>Well, I can tell you</i>
<i>the area has been sealed off.</i>

57:17.268 --> 57:21.578
<i>I've also been assured</i>
<i>that the public</i>
<i>is not in danger.</i>

57:21.613 --> 57:24.911
<i>Now, the suspect inside</i>
<i>that Wells Fargo</i>
<i>told us he's a marine,</i>

57:24.946 --> 57:29.718
<i>and we've worked</i>
<i>with several agencies</i>
<i>to confirm that he is in fact</i>

57:29.753 --> 57:32.721
<i>Lance Corporal</i>
<i>Brian Brown-Easley.</i>

57:33.218 --> 57:34.558
Daddy.

57:35.924 --> 57:36.956
Huh?

57:39.158 --> 57:43.127
<i>...our own Lisa Larson had</i>
<i>with the former marine.</i>

57:49.905 --> 57:53.577
<i>I just want to say...</i>
<i>He's calm and composed</i>

57:53.612 --> 57:55.645
<i>and came across as caring.</i>

58:23.268 --> 58:24.872
<i> Gandalf?</i>

58:24.907 --> 58:26.236
<i> No.</i>

58:26.271 --> 58:27.974
<i> Gimli?</i>

58:28.009 --> 58:29.613
<i> One guess left.</i>

58:29.648 --> 58:31.307
<i> Okay, Gollum.</i>

58:31.342 --> 58:33.276
Does she look like a Gollum?

58:44.927 --> 58:46.124
Hello?

58:46.159 --> 58:47.697
<i>Hi, is this Mr. Easley?</i>

58:49.096 --> 58:51.261
<i>Who am I speaking with?</i>

58:51.296 --> 58:54.935
<i>This is Eli Bernard,</i>
<i>chief negotiator</i>
<i>for Marietta PD.</i>

58:56.070 --> 59:00.171
<i> Chief?</i>
<i>Damn, they sent me the big dog.</i>

59:00.206 --> 59:02.140
<i>I'm actually a sergeant,</i>
<i>but that doesn't matter.</i>

59:03.143 --> 59:05.110
<i>I'm just pleased</i>
<i>to be talking to you.</i>

59:05.849 --> 59:06.881
Why you pleased?

59:06.916 --> 59:08.685
<i>I like to help people.</i>

59:08.720 --> 59:11.248
<i>And it looks like</i>
<i>you can use some help today.</i>

59:11.283 --> 59:14.218
Yeah, you the chief.
Then we good, man.

59:14.253 --> 59:17.254
People know the truth
when they hear it.
<i>I do agree.</i>

59:17.289 --> 59:21.632
My mama said show me a liar
and I'll show you a thief.

59:21.667 --> 59:23.832
<i> Mine said the same.</i>
Right.

59:23.867 --> 59:28.100
<i>-Your mama sound</i>
<i>like a smart woman.</i>
-Oh, she's smart. She was.

59:29.708 --> 59:31.642
I'm sorry.
<i>No. No sorries.</i>

59:31.677 --> 59:34.040
We all die
at our appointed time.

59:34.075 --> 59:37.307
Yes, we do. So tell me, Brian,
what can I do for you today?

59:37.342 --> 59:39.881
Is it okay
if I call you Brian?
<i>Absolutely. Uh--</i>

59:41.379 --> 59:43.412
<i>Sir, I know</i>
<i>you know why I'm here.</i>

59:43.447 --> 59:47.185
<i>And I just simply want</i>
<i>my money back. That's all.</i>

59:47.220 --> 59:49.825
From the VA, right?
<i>Yes, sir.</i>

59:49.860 --> 59:53.191
Yeah, I've had some problems
with Veteran Affairs myself.

59:53.226 --> 59:56.898
It's difficult
when they drag their feet.
<i>Right.</i>

59:56.933 --> 59:58.966
<i>Hey, what branch of service</i>
<i>you in?</i>

59:59.705 --> 01:00:00.935
Marine.

01:00:00.970 --> 01:00:02.365
<i>Semper fi, sir.</i>

01:00:03.907 --> 01:00:05.808
Where'd you train?

01:00:05.843 --> 01:00:07.403
<i>I'm a West Coaster.</i>

01:00:07.438 --> 01:00:09.075
<i>MCRD, San Diego.</i>

01:00:09.110 --> 01:00:11.242
Okay, okay.
So you one of them
Hollywood brothers

01:00:11.277 --> 01:00:12.815
with the veneers
in your mouth, huh?

01:00:14.082 --> 01:00:15.818
Shooting bubble gum bullets.

01:00:18.020 --> 01:00:20.020
I'm from St. Louis,
Missouri.

01:00:20.990 --> 01:00:23.727
But yes, sir,
a Hollywood marine I am.

01:00:24.994 --> 01:00:28.226
<i>So tell me, sir,</i>
<i>how can we put this back</i>
<i>in the VA's hands</i>

01:00:28.261 --> 01:00:29.997
<i>versus the bank tellers?</i>

01:00:32.430 --> 01:00:35.035
<i> Tell the VA</i>
<i>to send over the cash</i>
<i>and fix it.</i>

01:00:35.070 --> 01:00:36.773
<i>That's all, okay?</i>

01:00:38.040 --> 01:00:40.007
<i> Anything else</i>
<i>you need help with?</i>

01:00:42.847 --> 01:00:45.111
<i>Brian?</i>

01:00:45.146 --> 01:00:50.721
Yeah, I need you to help me
find the words to tell my
ex-wife and my daughter that...

01:00:52.417 --> 01:00:53.922
that I'm gonna die.

01:00:55.827 --> 01:00:58.124
<i>Sir, with all due respect,</i>

01:00:58.159 --> 01:01:01.457
<i>it is my responsibility</i>
<i>to make sure that you</i>
<i>get out of here alive.</i>

01:01:01.492 --> 01:01:03.162
Yeah, I understand,

01:01:03.197 --> 01:01:05.769
but we both know
they going to kill me, man.
They--

01:01:06.332 --> 01:01:08.266
We both know I'm dying here.

01:01:09.368 --> 01:01:10.906
You know.

01:01:10.941 --> 01:01:12.776
Ain't nothing for me out there
but bullets.

01:01:14.208 --> 01:01:17.110
At least everybody gonna know.
They gonna know how
the VA do, man.

01:01:17.145 --> 01:01:18.210
They gonna know.

01:01:19.279 --> 01:01:20.817
Everybody will see.

01:01:23.283 --> 01:01:25.481
<i>You said you had an ex-wife.</i>

01:01:25.516 --> 01:01:29.353
<i>I got one of those too.</i>
<i>Painful.</i>

01:01:29.388 --> 01:01:32.356
<i>Anybody else in your life</i>
<i>I can contact?</i>
Like a woman?

01:01:32.391 --> 01:01:34.292
<i>Yeah.</i>

01:01:34.327 --> 01:01:37.526
<i>I had but one</i>
<i>deep cut in my life,</i>
<i>and I married her.</i>

01:01:37.561 --> 01:01:38.967
Well done you, sir.

01:01:41.466 --> 01:01:42.938
She beautiful.

01:01:44.370 --> 01:01:47.404
Yeah, actually, uh,
I had thought about her...

01:01:49.540 --> 01:01:51.881
right at the moment
I decided to do...

01:01:53.852 --> 01:01:55.247
what I'm doing right now.

01:01:55.282 --> 01:01:57.216
<i>When was that moment, Brian?</i>

01:02:07.063 --> 01:02:10.394
Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!

01:02:11.969 --> 01:02:13.969
I don't wanna--
I'm not gonna leave!

01:02:14.004 --> 01:02:16.268
I'm not leaving until-- No!

01:02:16.303 --> 01:02:17.533
No!
Okay.

01:02:17.568 --> 01:02:19.942
I want my cash!
Take a breath.

01:02:19.977 --> 01:02:21.812
Where's my money?

01:02:28.579 --> 01:02:30.447
<i>In front of all those brothers.</i>

01:02:33.859 --> 01:02:36.486
I tried to go about it
the way we trained, but...

01:02:39.590 --> 01:02:41.898
sir, they've taken
everything from me.

01:02:43.594 --> 01:02:44.967
Everything.

01:02:47.169 --> 01:02:48.806
I apologize.

01:02:50.073 --> 01:02:51.303
<i>For what?</i>

01:02:52.439 --> 01:02:55.439
Well, that--
that another human being,
a fellow marine,

01:02:55.474 --> 01:02:57.573
<i>had to go through so much.</i>

01:02:57.608 --> 01:02:59.476
<i>How much money</i>
<i>does the VA owe you?</i>

01:03:00.919 --> 01:03:03.920
<i> $892.34.</i>

01:03:06.617 --> 01:03:07.517
That it?

01:03:08.520 --> 01:03:09.860
<i> Yes, sir.</i>

01:03:12.029 --> 01:03:15.162
<i>Sir, your honor's worth</i>
<i>more than $892.</i>

01:03:16.462 --> 01:03:19.331
You're worth more than $892.

01:03:20.037 --> 01:03:21.432
I'm worth nothing.

01:03:29.475 --> 01:03:30.980
I am nothing.

01:03:34.150 --> 01:03:36.117
I'm gonna die tonight...

01:03:38.319 --> 01:03:40.154
and nobody will care why.

01:03:41.124 --> 01:03:42.552
CNT's up and running.

01:03:42.587 --> 01:03:44.389
Let's get you in there
so we can hear y'all.

01:03:49.495 --> 01:03:50.560
Look...

01:03:52.564 --> 01:03:56.203
This is what we're going to do,
okay? Brother to brother.

01:03:56.238 --> 01:03:58.502
I'm gonna call your ex-wife
and daughter.

01:03:58.537 --> 01:04:01.439
I'ma tell her that
we have talked and we're
going to work this out.

01:04:01.474 --> 01:04:03.639
<i>Then I'm going to call you back.</i>

01:04:03.674 --> 01:04:05.080
<i>Is that okay?</i>

01:04:06.248 --> 01:04:08.248
Okay.
<i>Now, after I've done that,</i>
<i>Brian,</i>

01:04:08.283 --> 01:04:10.118
<i>I'm gonna need you</i>
<i>to do me a favor.</i>

01:04:10.153 --> 01:04:13.121
I'm going to need you
to let one of the ladies go.

01:04:13.717 --> 01:04:15.255
Can you do that for me?

01:04:17.655 --> 01:04:19.259
<i>Brian, you still there?</i>

01:04:20.658 --> 01:04:23.494
What about the cash?
What about the money?

01:04:23.529 --> 01:04:27.036
I give my word as a marine
and on my daddy,

01:04:27.071 --> 01:04:29.368
you let one of them go,
and we will sort this out.

01:04:31.108 --> 01:04:33.944
They're gonna come in that door
and crack my head open.

01:04:33.979 --> 01:04:36.947
Ain't nobody coming in there
and cracking open your skull,
man.

01:04:36.982 --> 01:04:39.213
No. No, no, sir.
Not on my word.

01:04:39.248 --> 01:04:41.413
Nigga, please, you don't
control these people, man.
You ain't got no power.

01:04:41.448 --> 01:04:44.251
Don't do that to me now.
Don't you underestimate me.

01:04:45.089 --> 01:04:46.220
Not me.

01:04:50.391 --> 01:04:53.689
I'm gonna call your family
and I'll call you back
in a moment.

01:04:54.329 --> 01:04:55.361
<i>All right?</i>

01:04:57.596 --> 01:04:58.628
Okay.

01:05:04.174 --> 01:05:09.980
Don't you ever, ever
disrespect me or cut me off
when I'm talking, sir!

01:05:11.148 --> 01:05:12.741
Give me the ex-wife's number.

01:05:12.776 --> 01:05:15.579
<i>A man has taken over</i>
<i>a Wells Fargo bank</i>

01:05:15.614 --> 01:05:17.548
<i>and is threatening</i>
<i>to blow it up.</i>

01:05:17.583 --> 01:05:21.684
<i>He apparently has an explosive,</i>
<i>some sort of backpack</i>
<i>or package--</i>

01:05:25.261 --> 01:05:27.624
Hello?
<i>Hello, Ms. Easley.</i>

01:05:27.659 --> 01:05:29.560
<i>I'm Sergeant Bernard</i>
<i>from the Marietta</i>
<i>Police Depart--</i>

01:05:29.595 --> 01:05:31.100
Is he dead?

01:05:31.135 --> 01:05:32.662
<i>No. No, ma'am.</i>

01:05:32.697 --> 01:05:35.005
<i>No, Brian is still</i>
<i>very much alive.</i>

01:05:37.207 --> 01:05:39.438
<i>Say, you got FaceTime?</i>

01:05:39.473 --> 01:05:41.770
Yeah.
<i>I just want you to see me.</i>

01:05:41.805 --> 01:05:44.509
Uh, yeah, I do. I do. I do.
Hold on.

01:05:46.216 --> 01:05:47.512
<i>Okay, good.</i>

01:05:47.547 --> 01:05:49.085
I am pressin' that button...

01:05:50.451 --> 01:05:53.254
right about... now.

01:05:53.289 --> 01:05:55.157
<i>Hi.</i>

01:05:55.192 --> 01:05:58.226
I gotta tell you,
I'm not too much
for all this technology,

01:05:58.261 --> 01:06:00.261
but let's just say
it's a pleasure to see you.

01:06:00.296 --> 01:06:01.757
Yeah.

01:06:01.792 --> 01:06:04.298
<i>First of all, I want to let</i>
<i>you and your daughter know</i>

01:06:04.333 --> 01:06:08.335
<i>I do this day in and day out,</i>
<i>and I know a good man</i>
<i>when I see one.</i>

01:06:08.370 --> 01:06:10.634
<i>Your husband's a good man.</i>

01:06:10.669 --> 01:06:14.407
Yeah. Yeah, I know that.
I know that. He wouldn't--
He wouldn't hurt a spider.

01:06:14.442 --> 01:06:17.443
<i>He has these episodes,</i>
<i>sometimes,</i>

01:06:17.478 --> 01:06:19.775
<i>but nothing like this,</i>
<i>nothing this bad.</i>

01:06:19.810 --> 01:06:22.052
Has he ever been violent
towards you or your daughter?

01:06:22.087 --> 01:06:25.616
<i>Violent? No. No. Hell, no.</i>
<i>He loves that child</i>
<i>with his whole heart.</i>

01:06:25.651 --> 01:06:27.585
<i>That's good to know.</i>

01:06:27.620 --> 01:06:30.555
<i>And before I go,</i>
<i>is there anything</i>
<i>I can help you with?</i>

01:06:30.590 --> 01:06:34.064
Yeah. Yeah, you can tell me
why the FBI is on their way
to my house.

01:06:34.099 --> 01:06:36.429
I didn't-- I didn't--
I didn't do anything wrong.

01:06:36.464 --> 01:06:39.300
I apologize, ma'am.
That's just procedure.

01:06:39.335 --> 01:06:41.137
This here's my number.

01:06:41.172 --> 01:06:43.601
If they do anything
you don't like,
you just call me.

01:06:44.340 --> 01:06:45.372
Make sense?

01:06:45.407 --> 01:06:46.538
<i>Yeah, it does.</i>

01:06:47.607 --> 01:06:49.739
<i>Is there anything</i>
<i>you want me to tell Brian?</i>

01:06:50.610 --> 01:06:51.642
Yeah.

01:06:52.447 --> 01:06:54.282
Yeah, tell him that I--

01:06:54.317 --> 01:06:57.813
Tell him that Kiah says,
"Don't do nothing stupid."

01:06:59.850 --> 01:07:01.685
<i>Okay, ma'am.</i>

01:07:01.720 --> 01:07:03.522
<i>I'll make sure</i>
<i>to pass that along.</i>

01:07:03.557 --> 01:07:05.689
All right. Thank you.

01:07:05.724 --> 01:07:08.527
<i>You're welcome.</i>
<i>Bye now.</i>

01:07:23.181 --> 01:07:26.149
<i>Wells Fargo confirms,</i>
<i>cameras live any moment now.</i>

01:07:29.319 --> 01:07:32.386
<i> All units,</i>
<i>suspect does not leave</i>
<i>the perimeter with the bomb.</i>

01:07:37.921 --> 01:07:41.428
<i> Hey, Brian.</i>
<i>I spoke to your ex-wife, man.</i>

01:07:41.463 --> 01:07:44.431
We actually video talked, but--
<i>Good, you did?</i>

01:07:44.466 --> 01:07:45.696
She's a lovely lady.

01:07:46.501 --> 01:07:47.863
<i>They okay?</i>

01:07:47.898 --> 01:07:49.799
She and your daughter
are doing just fine.

01:07:49.834 --> 01:07:52.505
<i>Told Cassandra she can call me</i>
<i>if she needs anything.</i>

01:07:52.540 --> 01:07:54.672
That's mighty fine of you.
Did you call the VA too?

01:07:54.707 --> 01:07:56.707
<i>To tell the truth,</i>
<i>that's going to take some time.</i>

01:07:56.742 --> 01:07:58.775
But I did
what I said I was going to do,

01:07:58.810 --> 01:08:02.251
so, how about you release
one of those ladies?

01:08:02.286 --> 01:08:05.452
I'ma release both of them
when the money's in my account.

01:08:05.487 --> 01:08:07.784
I was really clear.
<i>You gave me your word, marine.</i>

01:08:07.819 --> 01:08:10.193
Now don't do that.
Do not do that.

01:08:10.228 --> 01:08:11.557
I did not reply, sir.

01:08:11.592 --> 01:08:13.724
Now, you got me there.
<i>Okay.</i>

01:08:14.892 --> 01:08:16.363
It's just, uh,

01:08:16.399 --> 01:08:17.694
<i>I care about you, Brian.</i>

01:08:17.729 --> 01:08:19.729
<i>I care about you</i>
<i>just as much as I care about</i>

01:08:19.765 --> 01:08:21.468
<i>what them ladies</i>
<i>must be going through.</i>

01:08:21.502 --> 01:08:22.832
<i> I understand</i>
<i>you're good at your job.</i>

01:08:22.867 --> 01:08:25.636
<i>But I need you to go do it.</i>
<i>Just call the VA.</i>

01:08:27.410 --> 01:08:31.247
<i> You went from</i>
<i>10% to 50% disability. Right?</i>

01:08:34.384 --> 01:08:35.416
How you know that?

01:08:36.518 --> 01:08:38.649
Well, the VA just
sent over your file.

01:08:38.685 --> 01:08:41.158
<i>You were hurt in Iraqi Freedom.</i>

01:08:42.425 --> 01:08:43.886
<i> Yeah, right again.</i>

01:08:43.921 --> 01:08:46.460
<i> It is a bitch</i>
<i>getting shot in the heat.</i>

01:08:48.299 --> 01:08:49.760
<i>You-- You were shot, right?</i>

01:08:49.795 --> 01:08:51.332
No, I was injured.

01:08:53.733 --> 01:08:57.569
I was. Which means
you're just like me.

01:08:58.474 --> 01:09:00.506
<i>You've been through worse.</i>

01:09:00.542 --> 01:09:03.774
<i>You just gotta</i>
<i>push through, Brian.</i>
<i>I'll be here to help.</i>

01:09:03.809 --> 01:09:05.908
I understand
that you having conversations

01:09:05.943 --> 01:09:08.548
that you're supposed
to be having with the VA,
but what you need to do,

01:09:08.582 --> 01:09:09.912
rather than trying to
straighten me out,

01:09:09.947 --> 01:09:13.223
<i>is call them,</i>
<i>then have them call me.</i>

01:09:13.258 --> 01:09:15.786
Because you know what you did?
You gave me your word, sir.

01:09:15.821 --> 01:09:17.854
You did that.

01:09:17.889 --> 01:09:21.429
So if that isn't
the conversation,
then we don't need to talk.

01:09:21.464 --> 01:09:23.233
<i>Come on, Brian.</i>

01:09:23.268 --> 01:09:24.926
They taught us
better than this.

01:09:24.962 --> 01:09:28.337
No, no, no, no.
<i>We can fix this.</i>
<i>This is human error.</i>

01:09:28.372 --> 01:09:30.569
I'm gonna die
because of that human error.

01:09:30.604 --> 01:09:31.636
Sleep on that.

01:09:39.482 --> 01:09:40.514
Shit.

01:09:48.953 --> 01:09:50.622
I'm here, my baby.

01:09:53.627 --> 01:09:55.331
Please don't answer that.
It's Brian.

01:09:55.366 --> 01:09:58.565
There'll be a moment
when you can.
Just not now.

01:09:58.600 --> 01:09:59.830
Hold on, baby.

01:10:06.905 --> 01:10:08.245
Come here.

01:10:15.320 --> 01:10:17.452
I understand he is a local,
but I cannot confirm that.

01:10:27.629 --> 01:10:29.728
<i>Hi, this is Cassandra Deets--</i>

01:10:38.101 --> 01:10:40.607
<i> Hey, Brian.</i>
<i>Don't put the phone down.</i>

01:10:40.642 --> 01:10:43.005
Since you didn't let those
ladies out, you can at least
let me speak to one of them.

01:10:47.451 --> 01:10:48.483
Hold on.

01:11:01.696 --> 01:11:02.860
Negotiator wants to talk.

01:11:06.503 --> 01:11:07.535
Estel.

01:11:12.674 --> 01:11:14.003
Hello.

01:11:14.038 --> 01:11:15.543
<i>Hi, who am I speaking with?</i>

01:11:15.578 --> 01:11:17.875
Estel Valerie.
<i>Hello, Ms. Valerie.</i>

01:11:17.910 --> 01:11:21.043
This is Sergeant Bernard.
Is everyone all right in there?

01:11:22.387 --> 01:11:23.881
No, we are not.

01:11:25.753 --> 01:11:27.555
What are you people
doing out there?

01:11:27.590 --> 01:11:29.359
<i>Ma'am, we're doing</i>
<i>everything we possibly can</i>

01:11:29.394 --> 01:11:31.394
<i>to get y'all out of there</i>
<i>safely.</i>

01:11:31.429 --> 01:11:34.364
Well, how long does it take
to put money
into a man's account?

01:11:34.399 --> 01:11:36.795
Estel, just please
try to stay calm.

01:11:39.437 --> 01:11:40.766
I'm perfectly calm.

01:11:42.440 --> 01:11:44.638
<i>Okay. We're trying, ma'am.</i>

01:11:46.169 --> 01:11:48.543
Well, try harder, please.

01:11:52.648 --> 01:11:55.913
WSB-TV tip-line.
This is Lisa Larson.
What's your tip?

01:12:01.558 --> 01:12:04.086
Absolutely.
Uh, what is your address?

01:12:05.727 --> 01:12:07.628
<i>The remaining feed is up now.</i>

01:12:09.830 --> 01:12:11.665
Can you put Brian
back on the phone, please?

01:12:19.004 --> 01:12:20.707
<i> Hello?</i>

01:12:20.742 --> 01:12:22.973
I'm about to leave this car
and go over to the van.

01:12:23.008 --> 01:12:24.975
When I'm out there,
is there anything you'd like?

01:12:27.144 --> 01:12:28.814
Maybe some smokes?

01:12:30.015 --> 01:12:31.784
Okay. I can do that.

01:12:31.819 --> 01:12:33.148
<i>What kind do you like?</i>

01:12:33.183 --> 01:12:35.689
Newports. Newport Longs.

01:12:35.724 --> 01:12:37.493
Brian,
when I buy these cigarettes,

01:12:37.528 --> 01:12:39.825
someone is going to have to
leave them at the door for you.

01:12:39.860 --> 01:12:41.596
We got a plan for that?

01:12:41.631 --> 01:12:43.092
<i>Can't you do it?</i>

01:12:45.195 --> 01:12:47.602
Okay.

01:12:47.637 --> 01:12:50.671
You give me a few minutes
to buy those cigarettes,
and I-- I'll meet you there.

01:12:53.808 --> 01:12:55.544
That's some bullshit.

01:12:55.579 --> 01:12:56.875
I ain't going near that.

01:12:58.945 --> 01:13:00.417
You know what,

01:13:01.112 --> 01:13:02.584
they're not going to fix it.

01:13:03.180 --> 01:13:04.949
I will.

01:13:04.984 --> 01:13:08.183
I'm going to put your money
directly into your account.

01:13:08.218 --> 01:13:12.121
That's not what
I need to happen.
So, no, thank you.

01:13:14.697 --> 01:13:15.960
Money is money.

01:13:17.766 --> 01:13:20.129
Why you care about
where it comes from?

01:13:20.164 --> 01:13:22.901
If I cared about the money,
I'd have had you do that
when I walked in, but I didn't.

01:13:22.936 --> 01:13:24.573
So, no, I do not need that.

01:13:24.608 --> 01:13:27.004
You think the VA
got their own printed money?

01:13:27.809 --> 01:13:29.171
We're the bank.

01:13:30.108 --> 01:13:31.206
We get it back.

01:13:33.551 --> 01:13:34.913
No.

01:13:34.948 --> 01:13:36.211
I want their money.

01:13:40.624 --> 01:13:42.118
So you set on dying?

01:13:46.927 --> 01:13:49.829
How many times
I gotta hide my son
from the news?

01:13:53.263 --> 01:13:54.669
I'll tell you what.

01:13:55.838 --> 01:14:00.070
When he asks me,
"What did you do
to stop him from dying?"

01:14:04.010 --> 01:14:05.746
I'm gonna look him in the eye...

01:14:08.080 --> 01:14:09.915
and know that I tried.

01:14:18.860 --> 01:14:21.091
Please...

01:14:21.126 --> 01:14:26.965
...let me put what you're owed
into your account,

01:14:27.000 --> 01:14:29.264
and let's please go home.

01:14:33.171 --> 01:14:35.611
Look, you can bump it
to your-- your wife.

01:14:36.240 --> 01:14:37.778
Or your daughter.

01:14:40.816 --> 01:14:44.950
I don't care,
but I need you not to die.

01:14:46.349 --> 01:14:47.656
Okay, Brian?

01:14:50.122 --> 01:14:54.091
Brian,
I need you not to die.

01:14:57.261 --> 01:14:58.766
Not today.

01:15:02.299 --> 01:15:03.540
Okay.

01:15:07.238 --> 01:15:09.909
I'm gonna handle this. Right?

01:15:13.211 --> 01:15:14.815
I should probably--

01:15:16.720 --> 01:15:18.082
If I'm gonna
leave her something,

01:15:18.117 --> 01:15:20.282
I should probably
call Kiah, right?
Mm-hmm.

01:15:20.317 --> 01:15:22.185
You need some credit
on-- on the phone?

01:15:22.220 --> 01:15:24.286
-Yes, ma'am, I do.
-Okay. That's on me.

01:15:24.321 --> 01:15:27.025
Okay.
I'ma need that number, okay?

01:15:35.904 --> 01:15:38.366
Estel might be losing it.

